        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0665P0_20041018_GCR_348' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 218, line 10, at end insert&#x2014;
        <q>( ) Where tax information disclosed to OPRA is obtained by the Regulator by virtue of subsection (2), subsection (3) does not apply and subsections (3) and (4) of section 82 apply as if that information had been disclosed to the Regulator by virtue of subsection (2) of that section.</q>
